snippet.title: Unpacking Early Gameplay Footage
snippet.description:
Early work-in-progress footage of Unpacking, a zen puzzle game about the familiar experience of pulling possessions out of boxes and fitting them into a new home.

join our mailing list https://www.unpackinggame.com/
